  * Fix DEB_HOST_ARCH logic in debian/rules.
  * Adjust eclipse-cdt dependencies:
    o switch from eclipse-pde to eclipse-platform (Closes: #385350)
    o add gcc and make, as eclipse-cdt is pretty useless without them
    o suggest g++

